         I always prefer AoD over Shissar.  The str and AC makes a much bigger diff than a tiny % of haste.</P><P> Our pets are not broken or useless.  I do agree that something needs to be done about high AC mobs, pet has a tough time there, but overall I love Jobober.  Sure hes a bit light on hps, and could use some more attack, but look at other classes.  Sure Mages and Beastlords pets are stronger.  So what?  They cannot support thier pet like we do.  They have no crowd control, no escape (other than sow/jboots/gate for mage), no mana regen.  The list goes on and on.  Yes we are a pet class .. but the fact that we can go from 50-60 and never even conjure one if we like says a whole lot about our class.  The other pet classes NEED thier pet.  We dont.</P><P><b><font color=blue>Retrievil Hesevil</font id=blue></b><BR><font color=red><b>58 DE Necromancer - Tallon Zek</font id=red></b><BR><font color=blue><b>53 Iksar Necromancer - Rodcet Nife</b></font id=blue><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=333155" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=333155</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
